OL,3,CSmuggler who claims gang threatened to
OL,4,Cset mother's house on fire jailed
OL,6,FA man who imported nearly 70 grams of
OL,7,Flow-purity cocaine into Jersey last
OL,8,Fautumn has been jailed.
OL,10,FFindlay John Mackay, 27, was sentenced
OL,11,Fto four years and four months in
OL,12,Fprison by Jersey's Royal Court.
OL,14,FHis defence told the court that Mackay
OL,15,Fhad been pulled into a car in Glasgow
OL,16,Fby four men who threatened to set fire
OL,17,Fto his mother's house if he did not
OL,18,Ftake the drugs to Jersey.
