OL,3,CSmuggler who claims gang threatened to
OL,4,Cset mother's house on fire jailed
OL,6,FThe cocaine, which was 9.8% purity,
OL,7,Fwould have had an estimated street
OL,8,Fvalue of up to #17,500 and was mostly
OL,9,Fsmuggled inside him.
OL,11,FThe court heard that Mackay arrived on
OL,12,Fa flight from Glasgow with his
OL,13,Fgirlfriend at the beginning of October
OL,14,F2025, when customs officers at Jersey
OL,15,FAirport stopped and searched him.
OL,17,FThey uncovered a packet containing a
OL,18,Fwhite substance on him, which was
OL,19,Flater confirmed as cocaine.
