OL,3,CSmuggler who claims gang threatened to
OL,4,Cset mother's house on fire jailed
OL,6,FSeveral more packets of the same Class
OL,7,FA drug were found inside Mackay
OL,8,Ffollowing subsequent searches.
OL,10,FMackay's girlfriend told officers the
OL,11,Fpair were in Jersey to visit his
OL,12,Fgrandmother, which was later found out
OL,13,Fto be a lie since she no longer lived
OL,14,Fin the island.
OL,16,FDuring further investigations, Mackay
OL,17,Fclaimed he did not know the substance
OL,18,Fwas cocaine and that the only reason
OL,19,Fhe had trafficked the packets into
OL,20,FJersey was to pay off #10,000 of drug
OL,21,Fdebts.
