OL,6,FThe court also heard that Mackay was
OL,7,Finstructed to book a room for four
OL,8,Fdays at a St Helier hotel and to meet
OL,9,Fsomeone he claims he did not know at a
OL,10,Ffast food restaurant to hand over the
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,FThe defence said Mackay has struggled
OL,14,Fwith a series of mental health issues
OL,15,Fsince 2013, when his father was
OL,16,Fmurdered, and that he regretted
OL,17,Fimporting the drugs.
